snippet.title: Murder Next Room Teaser
snippet.description:
You are trapped in a location with others and one or more of them are killers. The police has been called and in the mean time try to survive. You can try to report the killer but there is no guarantee that the phones will be working.

Steam Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2158210/Murder_Next_Room/
